data.description: Beautiful brick home located within walking distance of the Bluegrass Yacht and Country Club and Bluegrass Marina. New roof 2023. New garage door and kitchen sink 2021. All kitchen appliances and washer/dryer to convey with suitable offer. Kitchen has custom cabinets and reverse osmosis system. HOA covers all yard maintenance. Built-ins can be found in guest BR/office and also in bonus room. Walk in attic and crawlspace for additional storage. Additional cabinet space in both utility room and garage. Additional features include 10ft ceilings and fire place in living room, triple trey ceiling and walk in closet in primary BR, Bonus Room has a half bath. Convenient to shopping and dining. Easy Nashville commute.
